        "content": "#include <stdio.h>\n#include <string.h>\n\nvoid reverse(char* str) {\n    char *start = str;\n    char *end = str + strlen(str) - 1;\n    char temp;\n    while (start < end) {\n        temp = *start;\n        *start = *end;\n        *end = temp;\n        start++;\n        end--;\n    }\n}\n\nint main() {\n    char str[101];\n    int i = 0; char c;\n    while (i < 100 && (c = getchar()) != '\\n' && c != EOF) str[i++] = c;\n    str[i] = 0;\n    if (i > 0) {\n        reverse(str);\n        printf(\"%s\\n\", str);\n    }\n    return 0;\n}\n"
